title: Emptying the Dirt Cup: Easy Lite Cyclonic Quick Vac UD20005
transcripts: Two empty the dirt cup put the cleaner into the upright position and turn the power off. Press the release button on the handle to remove hold the dirt cup over a trash can and press the quick release button to empty. Make sure the opening is clear of debris. Close the bottom and put the dirt cup back into the cleaner. The maintenance section will show you how to disassemble and clean the inside of the dirt cup. It is also important to clean the filter after every use and replace the filter every six months depending on use. There is a separate video that will show you how to clean the filters.
